    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-08-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-08-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="514" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d514">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Sir
                                    <persName type="to">Julian Pauncefote</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-08-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 22,
                                1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to my note to you of the 23d
                            ultimo, relative to the proposed agreement of arbitration of certain
                            matters affecting the seal fisheries in Behring Sea, I would be
                            extremely obliged if you would be kind enough to inform me when an
                            answer to the same may be expected.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William F. Wharton</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
